                                    <div class="svg-wraper"><a class="social_share" href="http://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=https://alj.com/en/media-news/j-wafs-develops-low-cost-handheld-technology-monitor-milk-quality-safety/&amp;t=J-WAFS develops low-cost handheld technology to monitor milk quality and safety">
                                        <!-- <svg width="20" height="22">
                                            <use fill="#8f8f90" stroke="#8f8f90" xlink:href="#share"></use>
